Actions

GetWirelessSchedulerSettings

http://linksys.com/jnap/wirelessscheduler/GetWirelessSchedulerSettings
This action gets the router's wireless scheduler settings.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

This action does not have any input parameters.

Output Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
isWirelessSchedulerEnabled bool no Whether wireless scheduler features are currently enabled.
wirelessSchedule WirelessSchedule no The schedule specifying when wireless access should be allowed and blocked during each calendar week.
configuredRadios ConfigurableRadio[] no The radios affected by the wireless scheduler
configurableRadios ConfigurableRadio[] no The configurable radios on the router

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/wirelessscheduler/GetWirelessSchedulerSettingsResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
_ErrorAbortedAction
_ErrorInvalidInput
_ErrorInvalidOutput
_ErrorNotReady
_ErrorSessionVerification
_ErrorUnauthorized
_ErrorUnexpected
_ErrorUnknownAction
_ErrorUnknownSession

SetWirelessSchedulerSettings

http://linksys.com/jnap/wirelessscheduler/SetWirelessSchedulerSettings
This action sets the router's wireless scheduler settings.

Note:

This action is safe to call within the context of a transaction.

Input Parameters

Name Type Optional Description
isWirelessSchedulerEnabled bool no Whether wireless scheduler features should be enabled.
wirelessSchedule WirelessSchedule no The schedule specifying when wireless access should be allowed and blocked during each calendar week.
configuredRadios ConfigurableRadio[] no The radios affected by the wireless scheduler

Output Parameters

This action does not have any output parameters.

Result

http://linksys.com/jnap/wirelessscheduler/SetWirelessSchedulerSettingsResult
Value Description
OK Success.
Error
ErrorInvalidConfiguredRadio The specified settings contain an invalid configurable radio.
ErrorInvalidWirelessSchedule The specified settings contain an invalid wireless schedule.

Structures

ConfigurableRadio

http://linksys.com/jnap/wirelessscheduler/ConfigurableRadio

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
radioID string no The unique identifier of the radio. This value never changes for a particular radio, and no two radios is the same wireless access point will have the same radio ID.
isGuestRadio bool no Whether the radio specified by the radioID is a guest radio.

WirelessSchedule

http://linksys.com/jnap/wirelessscheduler/WirelessSchedule
This service provides access to a router's wireless scheduler settings. A schedule specifying when wireless access should be enabled during a calendar week.
Each string member represents a wireless access schedule for a day of the week. The string must be exactly 48 characters long. Each character represents a 30-minute interval during the day, beginning at midnight. A "0" character indicates that wireless access should be blocked during the interval; a "1" indicates that wireless access should be allowed. No other characters may appear in the string. For example, the following string indicates that wireless access should only be allowed between 9 AM and 9 PM:
"000000000000000000111111111111111111111111000000"

Structure Members

Member Name Type Optional Description
sunday string no
monday string no
tuesday string no
wednesday string no
thursday string no
friday string no
saturday string no
